   <widget class="QTextEdit" name="textEdit">
    <property name="enabled">
     <bool>false</bool>
    </property>
    <property name="geometry">
     <rect>
      <x>110</x>
      <y>100</y>
      <width>411</width>
      <height>351</height>
     </rect>
    </property>
    <property name="styleSheet">
     <string notr="true">
    QTextEdit {
        background: transparent;
        font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;
        font-size: 10pt;
        border: none;
    }
</string>
    </property>
    <property name="html">
     <string>&lt;!DOCTYPE HTML PUBLIC &quot;-//W3C//DTD HTML 4.0//EN&quot; &quot;http://www.w3.org/TR/REC-html40/strict.dtd&quot;&gt;
&lt;html&gt;&lt;head&gt;&lt;meta name=&quot;qrichtext&quot; content=&quot;1&quot; /&gt;&lt;style type=&quot;text/css&quot;&gt;
p, li { white-space: pre-wrap; }
&lt;/style&gt;&lt;/head&gt;&lt;body style=&quot; font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:10pt; font-weight:400; font-style:normal;&quot;&gt;
&lt;p align=&quot;center&quot; style=&quot; margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px; line-height:138%;&quot;&gt;&lt;a name=&quot;docs-internal-guid-49d916bd-7fff-5be8-a28f-d95242e6b1db&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size:16pt; font-weight:600; color:#000000; background-color:transparent;&quot;&gt;S&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size:16pt; font-weight:600; color:#000000; background-color:transparent;&quot;&gt;cientific Contributions and Interests&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p align=&quot;justify&quot; style=&quot; margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size:11pt; color:#000000; background-color:transparent;&quot;&gt;Rizal’s exile in Dapitan also gave him the opportunity to pursue his scientific interests. He conducted various scientific experiments in fields like &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size:11pt; font-weight:600; color:#000000; background-color:transparent;&quot;&gt;botany&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size:11pt; color:#000000; background-color:transparent;&quot;&gt; and &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size:11pt; font-weight:600; color:#000000; background-color:transparent;&quot;&gt;zoology&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size:11pt; color:#000000; background-color:transparent;&quot;&gt;, studying the local flora and fauna. He collected specimens of plants, insects, and animals, and even sent them to European institutions, earning respect among his peers in the scientific community. His contributions to science, although less known compared to his revolutionary efforts, reflect his multi-faceted genius and determination to leave a positive mark on society, even in a quiet, isolated setting.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/body&gt;&lt;/html&gt;</string>
    </property>
   </widget>
   <widget class="QTextEdit" name="textEdit_2">
    <property name="enabled">
